  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 55,
      "chapterTitle": "炮击金门",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "34223948_55_4495-4599",
          "range": "4495-4599",
          "rangeStart": 4495,
          "rangeEnd": 4599,
          "markText": "在大规模的炮击停止之后，毛泽东请人给台湾领导人带话，表示只要蒋氏父子能抵制美国，我们可以同他合作；台、澎、金、马要整个回来，可以照原有方式生活，军队可以保存，继续搞三民主义。后来被周恩来概括成为“一纲四目”。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1710579842,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-16 17:04:02",
          "chapterUid": 55,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34223948&chapterUid=55&rangeStart=4495&rangeEnd=4599",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8ba32b00720a374c8baa538?chapterUid=55&rangeStart=4495&rangeEnd=4599"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 45,
      "chapterTitle": "开展“三反”“五反”运动",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "34223948_45_3110-3294",
          "range": "3110-3294",
          "rangeStart": 3110,
          "rangeEnd": 3294,
          "markText": "当年担任中央人民政府节约检查委员会主任的薄一波，有一段回忆。他说：“回忆毛主席当年抓防腐蚀的斗争，真是雷厉风行，至今历历在目。他看准的事情，一旦下决心要抓，就抓得很紧很紧，一抓到底，从不虎头蛇尾，从不走过场。他不仅提出方针，而且亲自督办；不仅提出任务，而且交代办法。在‘三反’运动紧张的日子里，他几乎每天晚上都要听取我的汇报，甚至经常坐镇中节委，参加办公会议，亲自指点",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1710579842,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-16 17:04:02",
          "chapterUid": 45,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34223948&chapterUid=45&rangeStart=3110&rangeEnd=3294",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8ba32b00720a374c8baa538?chapterUid=45&rangeStart=3110&rangeEnd=3294"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 59,
      "chapterTitle": "大兴调查研究之风",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "34223948_59_447-493",
          "range": "447-493",
          "rangeStart": 447,
          "rangeEnd": 493,
          "markText": "我这个人就是官做大了。我从前在江西那样的调查研究，现在就做得很少了。今年要做点调查研究工作。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1710579841,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-16 17:04:01",
          "chapterUid": 59,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34223948&chapterUid=59&rangeStart=447&rangeEnd=493",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8ba32b00720a374c8baa538?chapterUid=59&rangeStart=447&rangeEnd=493"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 58,
      "chapterTitle": "写出《十年总结》",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "34223948_58_4021-4028",
          "range": "4021-4028",
          "rangeStart": 4021,
          "rangeEnd": 4028,
          "markText": "布加勒斯特事件",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1710579840,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-16 17:04:00",
          "chapterUid": 58,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34223948&chapterUid=58&rangeStart=4021&rangeEnd=4028",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8ba32b00720a374c8baa538?chapterUid=58&rangeStart=4021&rangeEnd=4028"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "chapterTitle": "在国民党内工作",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "34223948_8_5190-5341",
          "range": "5190-5341",
          "rangeStart": 5190,
          "rangeEnd": 5341,
          "markText": "谁是我们的敌人？谁是我们的朋友？这个问题是革命的首要问题。中国过去一切革命斗争成效甚少，其基本原因就是因为不能团结真正的朋友，以攻击真正的敌人。革命党是群众的向导，在革命中未有革命党领错了路而革命不失败的。我们的革命要有不领错路和一定成功的把握，不可不注意团结我们的真正的朋友，以攻击我们的真正的敌人。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1710420945,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-03-14 20:55:45",
          "chapterUid": 8,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34223948&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5190&rangeEnd=5341",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8ba32b00720a374c8baa538?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5190&rangeEnd=5341"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 73,
      "chapterTitle": "临终的日子",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "34223948_73_441-550",
          "range": "441-550",
          "rangeStart": 441,
          "rangeEnd": 550,
          "markText": "我一生做了两件事情。一件是打倒了蒋介石，把蒋介石赶到台湾，战胜了日本帝国主义，把日本帝国主义赶出中国；一件是胜利地进行了无产阶级文化大革命。\n",
          "colorStyle": 5,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1708087464,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-02-16 20:44:24",
          "chapterUid": 73,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34223948&chapterUid=73&rangeStart=441&rangeEnd=550",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8ba32b00720a374c8baa538?chapterUid=73&rangeStart=441&rangeEnd=550"
        }
      ]
    }
